<div class="prose">

  <h1>Link to a CDN</h1>

  <p>
    You can link to the Unpoly files directly from a CDN:
  </p>

  <pre><code>&lt;script src="<%= cdn_link 'unpoly.min.js' %>"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;link rel="stylesheet" href="<%= cdn_link 'unpoly.min.css' %>"&gt;</code></pre>

  <h3>Linking with Bootstrap integration</h3>

  <p>If you want to use Unpoly's Bootstrap integration, you should **also** add the following links:</p>

  <pre><code>&lt;script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/g/unpoly@<%= guide.version %>(unpoly.min.js+unpoly-bootstrap3.min.js)"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/g/unpoly@<%= guide.version %>(unpoly.min.css+unpoly-bootstrap3.min.css)"&gt;</code></pre>

  <%= partial 'star_prompt' %>

</div>
